ResourceConfigItem.description:
Single configuration item with explicit unit.

Supports nested configs via List[List[ResourceConfigItem]] for complex
structures like lifecycle rules:

{"key": "lifecycle_rules", "value": [
  [
    {"key": "rule_name", "value": "TransitionToIA", "unit": null},
    {"key": "transition_days", "value": 30, "unit": "days"},
    {"key": "storage_class", "value": "STANDARD_IA", "unit": null}
  ]
], "unit": null}
